00:02:56.048 --> 00:02:58.054
So sine of zero.

00:02:58.054 --> 00:02:58.953
Well, that's zero.

00:02:58.953 --> 00:03:01.127
Just by looking at this first constraint,

00:03:01.127 --> 00:03:02.474
