00:03:06.157 --> 00:03:07.907
e to the zero is one.

00:03:09.274 --> 00:03:11.748
e to the zero is one

00:03:11.748 --> 00:03:15.032
and then the natural log of one plus zero,

00:03:15.032 --> 00:03:17.290
that's the natural log
of one which is a zero

00:03:17.290 --> 00:03:18.754
so that's out of the running.

00:03:18.754 --> 00:03:20.032
So just from that first constraint

00:03:20.032 --> 00:03:21.503
knowing that f of zero is equal to one,

00:03:21.503 --> 00:03:24.001
we're able to rule out two of the choices

00:03:24.001 --> 00:03:26.021
then knowing that the first derivative

00:03:26.021 --> 00:03:28.661
